I have a girlfriend, and
she is very important to me.

494
00:25:17,449 --> 00:25:19,748
It affects my life in every way.

495
00:25:20,719 --> 00:25:22,079
Probably should've
thought of that

496
00:25:22,121 --> 00:25:24,613
before you told her how
much her voice annoyed you.

497
00:25:25,224 --> 00:25:30,162
I said it didn't bother me.
